title: IDIOCY Season 2 [Stupid Humor]
description:
Before I say anything else, I want everyone to know that the quality of these recordings are bad on purpose...

Idiocy is a series of audio recordings my brother, Marcos, and I did in an attempt at comedy.

It&#039;s Stupid Humor, if you like that kind of thing.

I&#039;ve had a few people listen to it, and 4/5 said it was really funny. 3/5 even said it was marketable. 

Now then...

It&#039;s not TOO bad... we were just very inexperienced at editing, and recording, and stuff.

Season 1 is not here, because it&#039;s just too bad to share.
